fulltext: Upon  receipt_of_retract_command  the  controller  shall  within 2 minutes  satisfy  landing_gear_state = retracted & door_closed

semantics.ft: ((LAST V (((! (receipt_of_retract_command)) & ((! LAST) & (X (receipt_of_retract_command)))) -> (X ((F[<=2] (landing_gear_state = retracted & door_closed)) | (F[<2] LAST))))) & ((receipt_of_retract_command) -> ((F[<=2] (landing_gear_state = retracted & door_closed)) | (F[<2] LAST))))
semantics.ftExpanded: ((LAST V (((! (receipt_of_retract_command)) & ((! LAST) & (X (receipt_of_retract_command)))) -> (X ((F[<=2] (landing_gear_state = retracted & door_closed)) | (F[<2] LAST))))) & ((receipt_of_retract_command) -> ((F[<=2] (landing_gear_state = retracted & door_closed)) | (F[<2] LAST))))
semantics.ptExpanded: (H ((O[=2] (((receipt_of_retract_command) & ((Y (! (receipt_of_retract_command))) | (! (Y TRUE)))) & (! (landing_gear_state = retracted & door_closed)))) -> (O[<2] ((! (Y TRUE)) | (landing_gear_state = retracted & door_closed)))))
semantics.CoCoSpecCode: (H((OT(2,2,(((receipt_of_retract_command) and ((pre ( not (receipt_of_retract_command))) or FTP)) and ( not (landing_gear_state = retracted and door_closed))))) => (OT(2-1,0,(FTP or (landing_gear_state = retracted and door_closed))))))
semantics.description: ENFORCED: in the interval defined by the entire execution. TRIGGER: first point in the interval if (receipt_of_retract_command) is true and any point in the interval where (receipt_of_retract_command) becomes true (from false). REQUIRES: for every trigger, RES must hold at some point with distance <= 2 from the trigger (i.e., at trigger, trigger+1, ..., or trigger+2). If the interval ends sooner than trigger+2, then RES need not hold.
